snippet.title: Icarus Launch Date Announcement | 4K Gameplay Trailer - PC Gaming Show 2021
snippet.description:
An ICARUS gameplay trailer fresh from the #PCGamingShow at #E32021! #RTXon

ICARUS is a session-based PvE survival game for up to eight co-op players or solo. Explore a savage alien wilderness in the aftermath of terraforming gone wrong. Survive long enough to mine exotic matter, then return to orbit to craft more advanced tech for your next challenge. 

Pre order now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1149460/ICARUS/

Join our Discord:
https://discord.com/invite/surviveicarus

Follow us on Twitch:
https://www.twitch.tv/surviveicarus​
